content.raw:
Hi @kenta_uu , congratulations on your first commit! The file you are suggesting be added doesn't represent a complete model, please check the [How to contribute a model](http://gazebosim.org/tutorials?tut=model_contrib&cat=build_robot) tutorial for more detailed information.

Meanwhile, I'll decline this pull request so reviewers can focus on the other ones. Keep committing! :wink:
